```go
import "mahle/altium"
```

Read the data\.ogdl file \(produced by bom\.pas from the Altium PCB project\)\.

Format 3 specification \(as produced by bom\.pas\)

```
components
  D40A_1
    basename D40
    part D40_1
    code
```

NewBOM reads data\.ogdl and adds some nodes:

```
componentsCode
  CODE
    D40
partsCode
  CODE
    D40_1
```

